description:
This is model uses the exact same input as bimbostyleFour and bimbostyleFourU.

I was trained on SD_v1.5 which hopefully means that it's better applicable to other .ckpt in comparison to the normal "bimbostyleFour" and will trsy to emulate the style of the ckpt more than the deliberateV2 one

This lora is very responsive to body size prompts i.e. large breasts/wide hips/thick lips

And can also be used to bimbofie an existing model or lora

Combining this Lora together with One/Two/Three/Four in a "draw style" ckpt give great results and i can only recommend trying it out. (i don't know if the same applies to "real" ones as well)

can be mixed with every other bimbostyle

If you mix my models, i would recommend to always put the stronger weighted Lora in the front. i.e.

<lora:bimbostyleThree:0.5>:<lora:bimbostyleTwo:0.3>

Also i would go above a combined strength of 1 and from experience i would say .75-.9 is the sweet spot total strength
